1022
01:10:48,983 --> 01:10:52,433
- By God, I wish I knew. - By God, if you do not, who does?

1023
01:10:53,213 --> 01:10:56,413
Let us have pirates, clowns and a happy ending,>>

1024
01:10:56,913 --> 01:10:59,973
