1070
01:15:40,093 --> 01:15:42,563
My love is no lie.

1071
01:15:43,733 --> 01:15:46,263
I have a wife, yes,>>

1072
01:15:46,373 --> 01:15:49,433
and I cannot marry the daughter of Sir Robert De Lesseps.

1073
01:15:49,703 --> 01:15:53,043
You needed no wife come from Stratford to tell you that,>>

1074
01:15:54,813 --> 01:15:57,543
and yet, you let me come to your bed.

1075
01:15:57,983 --> 01:16:00,173
Calf-love.

1076
01:16:01,253 --> 01:16:04,243
I loved the writer and gave up the prize for a sonnet.

1077
01:16:05,753 --> 01:16:08,153
I was the more deceived.

1078
