He hears only that Juliet is dead.

1103
01:17:40,254 --> 01:17:43,073
And thus he goes to the apothecary...>>

1104
01:17:43,123 --> 01:17:45,053
That's me.

1105
01:17:45,123 --> 01:17:47,423
