1106
01:17:47,493 --> 01:17:50,553
He enters the tomb to say farewell to Juliet who lies there cold as death.

1107
01:17:52,493 --> 01:17:54,833
He drinks the poison.

1108
01:17:56,303 --> 01:17:58,773
He dies by her side,>>

1109
01:18:00,133 --> 01:18:02,863
