1113
01:18:18,023 --> 01:18:20,423
Sad... and wonderful.

1114
01:18:22,063 --> 01:18:24,923
I have a blue velvet cap that'll do well.

1115
01:18:24,993 --> 01:18:27,763
I've seen just such a cap on an apothecary.

1116
