1127
01:19:13,843 --> 01:19:16,573
It was the nightingale, and not the lark,>>

1128
01:19:16,683 --> 01:19:19,273
that pierced the fearful hollow of thine ear.

1129
01:19:19,353 --> 01:19:22,083
Nightly she sings on yon pomegranate tree.

1130
01:19:22,523 --> 01:19:25,313
Believe me, love, it was the nightingale.">>

1131
01:19:25,453 --> 01:19:28,393
"lt was the lark, the herald of the morn;>>

1132
01:19:29,593 --> 01:19:31,923
no nightingale.

1133
01:19:31,993 --> 01:19:34,793
Look, love, what envious streaks...>>

1134
