Therefore, stay yet.

1144
01:20:15,643 --> 01:20:18,043
Thou needst not to be gone.">>

1145
01:20:18,143 --> 01:20:20,403
"Let me be ta'en,>>

1146
01:20:20,473 --> 01:20:22,873
Iet me be put to death;>>

1147
01:20:23,643 --> 01:20:26,583
I am content, so thou wilt have it so.

1148
01:20:28,083 --> 01:20:30,483
I have more care to stay...>>

1149
01:20:30,753 --> 01:20:33,153
than will to go.

1150
01:20:33,223 --> 01:20:35,623
Come, death, and welcome.

1151
01:20:35,693 --> 01:20:38,353
Juliet wills it so.">>

1152
01:21:01,583 --> 01:21:04,113
You will go far, I fear.

1153
01:21:08,623 --> 01:21:11,153
I hope we work together again.

1154
01:21:13,863 --> 01:21:16,523
"Such mortal drugs I have, but Mantua's law...>>

1155
01:21:16,933 --> 01:21:19,923
is death, death to any he that utters them.">>

1156
01:21:21,517 --> 01:21:23,443
Then him. Then me.

1157
01:21:23,443 --> 01:21:24,595
Then him. Then me.

1158
01:21:24,645 --> 01:21:26,593
"Put-- Put this...>>

1159
01:21:26,643 --> 01:21:29,013
- in any liquid thing you will and--" - Hah!

1160
01:21:29,083 --> 01:21:31,543
What is it? What is it? What is it?

1161
01:21:33,383 --> 01:21:36,323
How silver sweet sound lovers' tongues by night.

1162
01:21:37,483 --> 01:21:40,483
- Like soft music-- - Shakespeare!

1163
01:21:57,473 --> 01:22:00,003
Upstart inky pup!

1164
01:22:00,097 --> 01:22:03,243
I'll show you your place, which is in hell!

1165
01:22:07,183 --> 01:22:10,383
- You're on my ground now! - By God, I'll fight the lot of you!

1166
01:22:10,653 --> 01:22:12,853
I am more than enough!

1167
01:22:20,193 --> 01:22:22,253
Move!

1168
