Absent friends.

1169
01:23:48,053 --> 01:23:50,713
This is the murderer of Kit Marlowe!

1170
01:23:51,959 --> 01:23:53,543
Will?

1171
01:23:53,593 --> 01:23:56,653
I rejoiced in his death because I thought it was yours! That is all I know of Marlowe!

1172
01:23:57,123 --> 01:23:58,993
Will?

1173
01:23:59,063 --> 01:24:00,723
Uh, it's true.

1174
01:24:00,793 --> 01:24:03,263
It was a... tavern brawl.

1175
01:24:03,603 --> 01:24:06,403
Marlowe attacked and got his own knife in the eye.

1176
01:24:08,673 --> 01:24:10,903
A quarrel about the bill.

1177
01:24:10,973 --> 01:24:13,703
The bill? Oh, vanity, vanity!

1178
01:24:14,313 --> 01:24:16,973
Not the billing, the bill!

1179
01:24:20,613 --> 01:24:22,733
Oh, God.

1180
01:24:22,783 --> 01:24:25,513
- I am free of it. - Where is she?

1181
01:24:26,327 --> 01:24:28,612
Close it.

1182
01:24:28,662 --> 01:24:32,943
