1183
01:24:32,993 --> 01:24:35,223
Take it down stone by stone.

1184
01:24:35,303 --> 01:24:38,093
I want it plowed into the ground and sown with quicklime!

1185
01:24:39,103 --> 01:24:41,003
Mr. Tilney, what is this?

1186
01:24:41,073 --> 01:24:43,473
Sedition and indecency.

1187
01:24:43,573 --> 01:24:46,303
